			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>The Panda&#8217;s Dresser is a two part design series for my soon to be T-shirt store <a href="http://minte.es">Minte&#8217;es</a>, The idea and inspirations for the design came from a past relationship, If it&#8217;s worthy of being called a realtionship.</p>
<p>The images are built up with items that relate directly to witnessing such a horrible person live alone, alone and away from the world due to fear her comsolive lies would cause more harm than what she already was bringing on herself.</p>
<p>The first image I call inside the dresser, is all that was signififant to our relationship, the money that was taken from me, the guitar pick repersenting the guitar that was taken to be borrowed without knowing 24 hours late I would be singel! and the notes symbolizing the empty promises, the &#8220;I love yous&#8221;, the &#8220;Will you marrie me this year because its a leap year&#8221; and the &#8220;You give me the best orgsm ever&#8221;.</p>
<p><a href="http://designerglue.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/inside.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-61" title="inside" src="http://designerglue.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/inside.jpg" alt="" width="510" height="492" /></a></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Image 2* says exactly what she&#8217;s doing right about now, There no point in explain what that image discribes.<a href="http://designerglue.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/The-Pandas-Toy.png"><br />
</a>The Panda&#8217;s Dresser was created with About Illustrator CS5 alone. And will soon be avalible for purchase as a Tshirt or  a canvas print.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>
